WEBVTT

00:00.300 --> 00:03.934
Quorum — the Nonprofit Board OS.

00:04.234 --> 00:13.772
The Launch Checklist is your roadmap — twenty-seven steps, in the order the law actually
works. Let's open it from the left menu.

00:14.072 --> 00:24.786
At the top, your progress card: eight of twenty-seven steps complete. Every box you tick
moves this number — and the ring on your Dashboard — forward.

00:25.086 --> 00:36.040
The steps are grouped into five stages, from forming the corporation all the way to
raising money. Each stage keeps its own little count, like two of two here.

00:36.340 --> 00:48.662
And every step is written in plain English. Under each title there's a short note: what
to do, where to go, and what it costs. No legal dictionary required.

00:48.962 --> 01:00.348
When a step has paperwork, the document is linked right there. See Adopt and certify the
Bylaws? Click Open, and the exact document appears.

01:00.648 --> 01:10.690
Finished something in real life? Click the circle next to it. Watch the counts update —
nine of twenty-seven, just like that.

01:10.990 --> 01:18.992
And don't feel rushed. One step at a time, in order, is exactly how this list is meant
to be walked.

01:19.292 --> 01:28.494
In the next five videos, we'll walk each stage together. First up: forming the
corporation, and getting your tax ID.
